	Fully covered domains:

		- fastly.com subdomains:

			- (www.)	(^ → www)
			- api
			- app
			- beacon
			- beta
			- blog
			- debug
			- maintenance

		- *.fastly.net:

			- control
			- mirrors
			- assets1.fastly.com.a.prod	(→ fastly.a.ssl.fastly.net)

			- *.a.ssl:

				- fastly
				- fastly-assets

		- *.imgix.net
		- *.parsecdn.com

